reviews.text: Bought  a portion of pound of char siu and lower portion duck for take away.  Char siu was very well done but  the duck was probably the worst I've had, despite specifically requesting lower portion, there was more bone than meat.  Would definitely go elsewhere for duck next time.  Char siu was good, juicy and packed with flavour.  Price was pretty good though, 88 HKD for a pound of char siu.
